  "remarks": "Leads a commission to register enemies of the Taliban as of mid-2013.\nBelieved to be in Afghanistan/Pakistan border area. Belongs to Nurzai tribe. Review\npursuant to Security Council resolution 1822 (2008) was concluded on 27 Jul.\n2010. INTERPOL-UN Security Council Special Notice web link:https://www.interpol.int/en/How-we-work/Notices/View-UN-Notices-Individuals",
